-----------------------------------------------------------

This was a bit too deep into the internals of [shapeless](https://github.com/milessabin/shapeless), but [Miles](https://twitter.com/milessabin) is a great speaker so it was quite fun, even if I didn’t get a lot of mileage out of it (yet). 

